ygData.subject: Re: Lute of the Gypsy Princess
ygData.msgSnippet: Personally I d love to have a lute of the gypsy princess, rather have the gypsy princess come to think of it, but you can t have everything.  Besides what
ygData.messageBody:
Personally I'd love to have a lute of the gypsy princess, rather have the
gypsy princess come to think of it, but you can't have everything. Besides
what could be more enchanting than:

Kitasi strums his fingers hauntingly across the Lute of the Gypsy
Princess...

Kitasi on E'ci
Purple Forever!!!

-----Original Message-----
From: Brandon Kassebaum [mailto:kassebaum@...]
Sent: Monday, June 28, 1999 10:15 AM
To: eqbards@onelist.com
Subject: Re: [eqbards] Lute of the Gypsy Princess


From: Brandon Kassebaum <kassebaum@...>

unfortunatly bub you just got a huge shaft. The lute does abso"lute"ly
nothing. Ouch.
Penaden
